    <item>
      <title>为了节省成本，壳牌将削减交易团队约 20% 的工作岗位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/shell-to-cut-about-20-of-jobs-in-deals-team-amid-push-for-cost-savings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，壳牌公司将在其交易团队中裁减至少 20% 的职位，因为该公司将继续重组其业务部门以降低成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/shell-to-cut-about-20-of-jobs-in-deals-team-amid-push-for-cost-savings</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:21:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称日本央行将考虑削减 ETF 购买，并继续购买债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/boj-is-said-to-mull-axing-etf-buys-continuing-bond-purchases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，日本央行官员正在考虑取消 2010 年推出的购买交易所交易基金的措施，前提是日本央行的通胀目标能够实现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-13/boj-is-said-to-mull-axing-etf-buys-continuing-bond-purchases</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 13 Mar 2024 09:15:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
